rows.label: qst701401_msg0001
rows.name: Adel-sama! Adel-sama!

rows.label: qst701401_msg0002
rows.name: Is that...Ivan?

rows.label: qst701401_msg0003
rows.name:
What's he doing here in the capital?
Has he got business here?

rows.label: qst701401_msg0004
rows.name: Could be.

rows.label: qst701401_msg0005
rows.name:
I asked him to distribute some food
supplies to the militia.

rows.label: qst701401_msg0006
rows.name: He's probably here to pick them up.

rows.label: qst701401_msg0007
rows.name:
True, Ivan was in charge of food
rations, wasn't he...

rows.label: qst701401_msg0008
rows.name: Which suits his interests just fine.

rows.label: qst701401_msg0009
rows.name: Hey, Ivan. Good work there!

rows.label: qst701401_msg0010
rows.name:
Come to fetch those food supplies,
have you?

rows.label: qst701401_msg0011
rows.name: That's right. Look at all this!

rows.label: qst701401_msg0012
rows.name:
It's enough to feed an army!
In fact, it will.

rows.label: qst701401_msg0013
rows.name:
We won't have to worry about food
shortages for a while, anyway.

rows.label: qst701401_msg0014
rows.name: Now you just have to get it to Aletta.

rows.label: qst701401_msg0015
rows.name: Yes. About that... There's a problem.

rows.label: qst701401_msg0016
rows.name:
We got through the desert without
much issue, but then...

rows.label: qst701401_msg0017
rows.name:
Then we encountered a whole host of
Tizza Parisax swarming all over the
Braying Canyon!

rows.label: qst701401_msg0018
rows.name:
We ran as fast as our legs could
carry us, all the way here.

rows.label: qst701401_msg0019
rows.name:
But that's not going to fly on the return
trip to Aletta...

rows.label: qst701401_msg0020
rows.name:
Because you'll be carrying a heavy
cargo.

rows.label: qst701401_msg0021
rows.name: Exactly.

rows.label: qst701401_msg0022
rows.name:
We were just discussing what to do
about it when you walked by!

rows.label: qst701401_msg0023
rows.name: Impeccable timing, I have to say!

rows.label: qst701401_msg0024
rows.name:
What are we talking about, then?
A little pest extermination?

rows.label: qst701401_msg0025
rows.name:
That does seem like the obvious
solution.

rows.label: qst701401_msg0026
rows.name: Is everyone on board for this?

rows.label: qst701401_msg0027
rows.name: Do you even have to ask?

rows.label: qst701401_msg0028
rows.name: Right!

rows.label: qst701401_msg0029
rows.name:
Wait here, Ivan. We'll be back in
a jiffy.

rows.label: qst701401_msg0030
rows.name: Thank you all!

rows.label: qst701401_msg0031
rows.name: And be careful!
